{"tid":2274224,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共華為向開拖瑞典 就被踢出瑞典5G市場一事提出上訴","createTime":"2020-11-06T09:50:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T08:07:52.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9d2252508ad7f3139e6fe0153f081117bfd09f0d","tid":2274224,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:50:24.000Z","msg":"華為就被瑞典禁止參與5G網絡建設提出上訴<br />\n<br />\n中國電訊設備製造商華為，已就瑞典禁止華為參與當地5G網絡建設提出上訴。瑞典郵政電訊管理局表示，已交由斯德哥爾摩法院處理。華為暫時未有回應。<br />\n<br />\n瑞典政府上月以國家安全為由，宣布禁止華為和中興參與當地5G網絡建設；華為批評決定不公平及不可接受，強調華為從未、亦永遠不會對瑞典的網絡安全造成丁點威脅，希望瑞典政府重新評估有關決定。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2365132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2365132&d=q9TyM%2Fq5ITgKOQyjXL1c9v8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=67b26dd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2365132</a>"},{"pid":"c8f61ed9dd2afbd9eac7ae24def0b980cd8664ba","tid":2274224,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以後瑞典有乜野唔用国貨都會被上訴"},{"pid":"c5e48ca64cfcafde0d37e6ca5f21685f706461be","tid":2274224,"uid":64901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:57:35.000Z","msg":"屌你老母自由市場，唔撚用你既野就告鳩你"},{"pid":"4005b2ac2491442f9196483baf5e987c97f099c8","tid":2274224,"uid":46947,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"愛立信就直接被中国禁止參與5G網絡建設。"},{"pid":"6ba89bb4288d61e4d4e07993c846343fb8dcd152","tid":2274224,"uid":286146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T08:06:57.000Z","msg":"咁易比你5G入瑞典偷機密咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b6a3dc5a96a632ca890ec4fb76ad220d93e152","tid":2274224,"uid":286146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4005b2ac2491442f9196483baf5e987c97f099c8","tid":2274224,"uid":46947,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T10:00:21.000Z","msg":"愛立信就直接被中国禁止參與5G網絡建設。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T08:07:52.000Z","msg":"愛立信咁高科技含量&nbsp;入左中國華為鬼有人用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}